for connecting to linux from aws server
	open command prompt
	ssh -i Key1.pem ec2-user@<public-ip-address>
details for ssh connection	
	-- we need public ip address, pem file(which is downloaded during creation of instance)

stop instance -- it just stops the server . here we can restart the machine ... 
	public ip changes if we restart the server
terminate instance -- it deletes the instance

